WEBVTT

00:00:01.070 --> 00:00:02.747
Davnih dana,

00:00:02.771 --> 00:00:04.519
bio sam profesionalni animator.

00:00:06.573 --> 00:00:07.723
(Glazba)

00:00:07.747 --> 00:00:09.653
[Eric Dyer]

00:00:09.677 --> 00:00:10.687
[Animator]

00:00:10.711 --> 00:00:11.861
[Stvaratelj]

00:00:16.425 --> 00:00:18.151
Po noći bih radio

00:00:18.175 --> 00:00:20.458
vlastite eksperimentalne filmove.

00:00:20.482 --> 00:00:21.519
(Glazba)

00:00:21.519 --> 00:00:26.124
I tako sam provodio mnogo vremena,
zbilja previše vremena, ispred ekrana,

00:00:26.124 --> 00:00:28.909
zbog posla koji će biti
prikazan na ekranu

00:00:28.933 --> 00:00:32.656
i osjećao sam veliku potrebu
da ponovno uposlim svoje ruke.